=== 笨瓜秀 pourquoi ===
謝鑫佑受社團法人台灣露德協會之邀<ref>{{Cite web|title=社團法人台灣露德協會2015年重點成果報告|url=https://www.twnpos.org.tw/upload/membersfiles2/160902164710.pdf|accessdate=|author=露德協會|date=2015年12月|format=|publisher=|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122181047/https://www.twnpos.org.tw/upload/membersfiles2/160902164710.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以十餘年的同運經驗於2015年10月22日起開設網路廣播節目「笨瓜秀 pourquoi」<ref>{{Cite web|title=笨瓜秀|url=https://hearthis.at/ron/|accessdate=2021-01-17|work=hearthis.at|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124140028/https://hearthis.at/ron/|dead-url=no}}</ref>每周四晚上21:00至22:00由[[中華電信|中華電信]][[Hi_Chennal|hiChennal]][[網路廣播|網路廣播]]live播出，且於2020年起，因應hiChennal訊號不再放送全球，粉絲專頁<ref>{{Cite web|title=笨瓜秀 pourquoi|url=https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Radio-Station/pourquoishow/about/|accessdate=2021-01-17|work=www.facebook.com|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126211707/https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Radio-Station/pourquoishow/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref>同步視訊直播，並更新於Podcasts<ref>{{Cite web|title=笨瓜秀 on Apple Podcasts|url=https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/%E7%AC%A8%E7%93%9C%E7%A7%80/id1436603385|accessdate=2021-01-17|work=Apple Podcasts|language=en-us|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122214823/https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/%E7%AC%A8%E7%93%9C%E7%A7%80/id1436603385|dead-url=no}}</ref>，聽眾遍及[[臺灣|臺灣]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]、[[香港|香港]]、[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]、[[尼泊爾|尼泊爾]]、[[中國|中國]]、[[日本|日本]]，甚至遠在[[法國|法國]]南部與[[英國|英國]]的華人。

節目內容包括[[同志_(LGBT)|同志 (LGBT)]]、[[愛滋|愛滋]]、[[人權|人權]]、自我認同與社會觀察，企圖打開聽眾的視野，讓世界各地知道台灣的[[性別平等|性別平等]]運動的境況。節目來賓包括：[[五月天|五月天]]石頭（[[石錦航|石錦航]]）、[[戴愛玲|戴愛玲]]、[[丁宁_(演员)|丁宁 (演员)]]、郭子（[[郭蘅忻|郭蘅忻]]）、[[鼓鼓|鼓鼓]]、陳秋山、[[丘沁偉|丘沁偉]]、呂秋遠、[[陳鎮川|陳鎮川]]、[[許佑生|許佑生]]、[[賴正哲|賴正哲]]、[[羅毓嘉|羅毓嘉]]、[[張耀升_(小說家)|張耀升 (小說家)]]、[[林于凱|林于凱]]、[[黃益中|黃益中]]、[[呂欣潔|呂欣潔]]、張懋禛、陳思豪、[[黃逸豪|黃逸豪]]、古育仲等。歌手[[戴安娜_(歌手)|戴安娜 (歌手)]]也曾於「JIN's Vlog」<ref>{{Cite web|title=出櫃擁抱自己 ft. 笨瓜秀主持人Ron｜【真心相談室】it's JIN's Vlog EP09|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dWVOprA658w|accessdate=|author=戴安娜|date=2019年5月28日|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021年1月23日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123111732/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dWVOprA658w|dead-url=no}}</ref>分享受訪出櫃經驗。

歷經4年5個月，該節目於2020年3月20日劃下句點，共製播164集，深獲網友喜愛與推薦<ref>{{Cite web|title=Podcast 推薦 (Podcast recommendation for English learning/Web Development/ Technology/ Fun)|url=https://medium.com/@mike1026915/podcast-%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6-podcast-recommendation-for-english-learning-web-development-technology-fun-59ecf888ec32|accessdate=2021-01-16|date=2019-08-09|last=Fang|first=Mike|work=Medium|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122013432/https://medium.com/@mike1026915/podcast-%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6-podcast-recommendation-for-english-learning-web-development-technology-fun-59ecf888ec32|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Athena Lam|url=https://shenchingtou.github.io/lgbtq/taiwan-queer-media/|accessdate=2021-01-16|work=shenchingtou.github.io|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124153206/https://shenchingtou.github.io/lgbtq/taiwan-queer-media/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾創下<u>hearthis.at</u>周收聽冠軍<ref>{{Cite web|title=[2017/1/5] 黃識恩【平權Ｘ保衛】|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2017-01-01&date-end=2017-01-08|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122054700/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2017-01-01&date-end=2017-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另有9集擠入全球周點播前10名<ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/01/07] 新年新希望！顧文瑋醫師帶來預防愛滋最新武器|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-01-03&date-end=2016-01-10|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122013311/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-01-03&date-end=2016-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/01/21] 用裸體做社會運動的BOBO|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-01-17&date-end=2016-01-24|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122181604/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-01-17&date-end=2016-01-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/2/18] 在尼泊爾開店的台灣旅人 蔚蔚|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-02-14&date-end=2016-02-21|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122025047/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-02-14&date-end=2016-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/8/4] Jay來示範熊熊也能做瑜伽|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-07-31&date-end=2016-08-07|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122054030/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-07-31&date-end=2016-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/10/20] 鵠翔的男妓體驗在⋯⋯明代|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2017-02-12&date-end=2017-02-19|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122020324/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2017-02-12&date-end=2017-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2016/11/24] 長老會牧師陳思豪【基督Ｘ同志】|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-11-20&date-end=2016-11-27|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122182656/https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2016-11-20&date-end=2016-11-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=[2017/1/12] 道道＆道媽【親情Ｘ彩虹】|url=https://hearthis.at/popular/?category=radioshow&date-start=2017-01-08&date-end=2017-01-15|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122051023/https://hearthis.at/popular/